To insert a picture into a document, drag&amp;drop Image element from right panel &gt; Palette Elements into the location in editor you want.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

*Add picture*

It is only allowed to insert a picture into editable area through drag&amp;drop in the Composer. The desired picture has to be chosen from existing pictures in the ICR on the server or uploaded into the ICR first. If it is already uploaded, just select the image (path) from the file picker dialog which helps you to find the path you are looking for. Filepicker is also available by double-clicking on the image in the editor.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

*Accessing filepicker to pick file*

Pictures can be uploaded via right-click ctx menu in the file picker dialog. There are limitations on uploading regarding the picture mime-type and file size.
